<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<title>Home</title>
	<!--[if lt IE 9]>
	<script src="http://html5shiv.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script>
	<![endif]-->
  
	<style type="text/css">
		.center {
		float: none;
		margin-left: auto;
	    margin-right: auto;
		}

		#sign-up
		{
		background-image: url(<%= asset_path('feet-image.jpg') %>);
		background-size: 100%;
	    background-repeat:no-repeat;
		height:800px;
		min-width: 900px;
		margin-top: -20px; /*hack for the top margin */s
		}

		#sign-up #sign-up-content
		{
		padding-top: 150px;
		}

		#sign-up #sign-up-content h1
        {
        margin:0px;
        display: block;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
        text-shadow: 2px 4px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
		font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
        font-size: 40px;
        }

        #sign-up #sign-up-content #sign-up-form
		{
        height: 250px;
        width:600px;
        position: relative;
        }
		
		#sign-up #sign-up-content #sign-up-form #sign-up-form-background
		{
        background: white;
        filter:alpha(opacity=20); /* IE */
        -moz-opacity:0.2; /* Mozilla */
        opacity: 0.2; /* CSS3 */
        border-radius: 8px;
        -moz-border-radius: 8px;
        -webkit-border-radius: 8px;
        }

        #sign-up #sign-up-content #sign-up-form #sign-up-form-content
		{
        padding: 50px 25px;
        }

        #sign-up #sign-up-content #sign-up-form #sign-up-form-background,
        #sign-up #sign-up-content #sign-up-form #sign-up-form-content
		{
        height: 100%;
        width:100%;
        position: absolute;
        }

        .marketing-message
		{
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        padding: 100px;
		margin: 0px;
		min-width: 900px;
        }

        .marketing-message div
		{
		width: 100%:
        height: 100%;
        }

		#developer
		{
		width: 900px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
		overflow: hidden;
		}

		.marketing-message-image
		{
		display: block;
		text-align: center;
		}

		.marketing-message-image .img-circle
		{
		border: 5px solid #e5e5e5;
		}

		.marketing-message img
		{
			width: 100%;
			max-width: 300px;
			min-width: 200px;
			margin-left: auto;
			margin-right: auto;
		}

        h2
		{
        margin:30px;
        display: block;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        text-align: center;
		font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
		font-size: 40px;
		}

        p
		{
        text-align:justify;
        font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
		font-size: 20px;
        line-height: 24px;
        margin: 20px;
        margin-left: 20px;
        margin-right: 20px;
        }

		a:hover
		{
		background-color: transparent;
		}

		.credit
		{
		height: auto;
		padding:10px;
		float: left;
		}
		
		.credit .content
		{
		background-color: white;
		width: 100%;
		height: auto%;
		}
	
		.credit .content img
		{
		background-color: white;
		width: 200px;
		height: 200px;
		margin: 20px;
		}

		.credit .content p
		{
		margin-top: -5px;
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 25px;
		}

        #footer
		{
        height: 100px;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 20px;
        }
            
        #footer img
		{
        height:50px;
        }

	</style>
</head>


<body>
	<!-- quick sign up -->
    <div id="sign-up">
		<div id="sign-up-content">
			<div class="center" style="width:650px; margin-bottom:20px;">
				<h1> Where will you be next summer? </h1>
            </div>
            <div id="sign-up-form" class="center">
                <div id="sign-up-form-background"></div>
                <div id="sign-up-form-content">                  
					<div class="form-group">
						<input type="email" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Your UTOR email address">
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="password" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Password">
                    </div>
                    <form>
						<button type="submit" class="btn btn-lg btn-warning pull-right">Sign Up</button>
                    </form>			
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="message-1" class="marketing-message row">
        <div class="marketing-message-image col-md-4 ">
            <img src="http://placehold.it/300x300">
        </div>
        <div class="marketing-message-content col-md-8 ">
            <h2>Need help with your upcoming interview?</h2>
            <p>We connect you with the upper years who have been in your shoe. They are willing to share their internship hunting experience and guide you through the journey.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="message-2" class="marketing-message row" style="background-color:#e5e5e5;">
        <div class="marketing-message-image col-md-4 ">
            <%= image_tag("marketing-1.png") %>
        </div>
        <div class="marketing-message-content col-md-8 ">
            <h2>Where have your peers been?</h2>
            <p>Google, Facebook, Microsoft, Bombardier, BCG, Deloitte, P&G... <b>Why can't YOU?</b> Starting from today, DREAM BIGGER, AIM HIGHER. Talk to the people who have been there, and learn from them. After all, "you miss 100% of the shots you don't take."</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="message-3" class="marketing-message row">
        <div class="marketing-message-image col-md-4">
            <%= image_tag("sq-logo.png") %>
        </div>
        <div class="marketing-message-content col-md-8 ">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Google, Facebook, Microsoft, Bombardier, BCG, Deloitte, P&G... <b>Why can't YOU?</b> Starting from today, DREAM BIGGER, AIM HIGHER. Talk to the people who have been there, and learn from them. After all, "you miss 100% of the shots you don't take."</p>
        </div>
    </div>

	<div id="message-4" class="marketing-message row" style="background-color:#e5e5e5; padding: 0px;">
		<h2>The Developers</h2>
		<div id= "developer" class="row">
		<div class="credit" style="width: 300px;">
			<div class="content row">
				<div class="marketing-message-image">
					<%= image_tag("ming-yi-bian.jpg", :class => 'img-circle')%>
				</div>
				<p> MingYi Bian </p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="credit" style="width: 300px;">
			<div class="content row">
				<div class="marketing-message-image">
					<%= image_tag("surprise-me.jpg", :class => 'img-circle') %>
				</div>
				<p> Matt Pua </p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="credit" style="width: 300px;">
			<div class="content row">
				<div class="marketing-message-image">
					<%= image_tag("louisa-chong.jpg", :class => 'img-circle') %>
				</div>
				<p> Louisa Chong </p>
			</div>
		</div>
		</div>
	</div>

    <div id="footer" style="background-color:#e5e5e5;">
		<%= link_to image_tag("social-facebook.png"), "https://www.facebook.com/UofTYoureNext"%>
        <%= link_to image_tag("social-twitter.png"), "https://twitter.com/UofT_YoureNext"%>
        <%= link_to image_tag("social-linkedin.png"), "http://www.linkedin.com/company/you're-next-career-network"%>
        <div id="company-logo" class="pull-right" style="margin-right: 10px; height: 100%">
            <%= image_tag("YNCN-boxes-text.png") %>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>